      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning, mint condition\u2014it basically looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so you won\u2019t find a single flaw anywhere. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and it's ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
