      "description": "This is an exceptional example of automotive preservation. Finished in its original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, the exterior is entirely devoid of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom fragrance; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear, and every switchgear component operates with a crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history and a driving experience that remains as tight and responsive as the day it was delivered. Garage-kept under a climate-controlled cover and never exposed to inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model. It is a true collector-grade masterpiece ready for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
