      "description": "Hey there! \ud83c\udf1f I am so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s in total mint condition\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message, I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
